source: TEXT_BANAMA307_01248_SEQ_00<tab>Yadovv Gah would burn the heart out of his enemies.
target: TEXT_BANAMA307_01248_SEQ_00<tab>Yadovv Gah a un plan pour saper le moral de l'ennemi.

source: TEXT_BANAMA307_01248_SEQ_01<tab>It is tradition for Amalj'aa to be buried with their weapons, for they are warriors in death as well as in life. Conversely, it is considered sacrilege for the weapons of the dead to be removed from their graves. Yadovv Gah has already seen to that dark deed; all that remains is for you to place the stolen weapons on display in Zahar'ak and show the Flamefangs that their fallen brothers have been disgraced.
target: TEXT_BANAMA307_01248_SEQ_01<tab>Yadovv Gah vous a confié une mission visant à démoraliser l'ennemi. Placez les <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E892A0302 /var> à cinq <var 33 ((EObj)) 0DF61E91050302 /var> du camp de Zahar'ak. Éliminez les <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF209050302 /var> qui pourraient essayer de vous gêner.

source: TEXT_BANAMA307_01248_SEQ_02<tab>As the cries of the Flamefangs echo in your ears, you realize that your monuments to their misery have achieved the desired effect. Report your success to Yadovv Gah.
target: TEXT_BANAMA307_01248_SEQ_02<tab>Vous avez pu planter les trophées aux endroits indiqués. Retournez faire votre rapport à Yadovv Gah.

source: TEXT_BANAMA307_01248_SEQ_03<tab>Recognizing that others may find his methods distasteful, Yadovv Gah asserts that by breaking the spirits of his sworn enemies, he ensures that they are less like to seek vengeance. Should his strategy prove effective, the conflict between the Brotherhood and the Flamefangs may end more quickly than anticipated.
target: TEXT_BANAMA307_01248_SEQ_03<tab>Yadovv Gah semble satisfait de l'opération. Il estime que le moral de l'ennemi en prendra un coup. Il vous demande de continuer à contribuer au succès de la Ligue des cendres.

source: TEXT_BANAMA307_01248_TODO_00<tab><var 08 E3E802E804 ((Make monuments with the stolen weapons in Zahar'ak.)) ((Make the final monument in Zahar'ak.)) /var>
target: TEXT_BANAMA307_01248_TODO_00<tab><var 08 E3E802E804 ((Placer les <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E892A0302 /var> aux cinq <var 33 ((EObj)) 0DF61E91050302 /var> de Zahar'ak)) ((Placer <var 33 ((EventItem)) 03F61E892A0202 /var> sur le dernier <var 33 ((EObj)) 0DF61E91050202 /var> et vaincre les ennemis qui pourraient apparaître)) /var>
TEXT_BANAMA307_01248_TODO_01<tab>Faire un rapport à Yadovv Gah

source: TEXT_BANAMA307_01248_YADOVVGAH_000_000<tab>Amalj'aa are warriors in death, as in life. For this reason, it is custom to be buried with one's weapons─
target: TEXT_BANAMA307_01248_YADOVVGAH_000_000<tab>Une troupe d'élite des Amalj'aa de Zahar'ak, les Crocs de Feu sont. Des adversaires de taille, ils constituent. Une détermination sans faille, face à eux nous devons montrer.

source: TEXT_BANAMA307_01248_YADOVVGAH_000_002<tab>Weapons such as these, which were taken from the graves of the Flamefangs. Aye, by this sacrilege we have brought great shame upon their fallen. But I would not have it end there.
target: TEXT_BANAMA307_01248_YADOVVGAH_000_002<tab>Puissant<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> guerri<var 08 E905 ((ère)) ((er)) /var>, une dé<var 16 /var>mon<var 16 /var>stra<var 16 /var>tion de force pour nos ennemis nous préparons. Planter des <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E892A0302 /var>, dans des endroits stratégiques bien visibles au cœur de Zahar'ak, nous allons<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANAMA307_01248_YADOVVGAH_000_003<tab>Make monuments of that which was stolen for all Zahar'ak to see! Show that no glory awaits them─in this life or the next.
target: TEXT_BANAMA307_01248_YADOVVGAH_000_003<tab>Plus précieuse que la vie, une arme est pour un Amalj'aa. Avec des prises de guerre ennemies, ces trophées sont fabriqués. Un affront plus humiliant que la mort, exposer au grand jour ces objets constitue<var 1D /var>! De leur faire goûter à cet opprobre, ta mission sera. Les éventuels gêneurs qui se présenteront sur ton chemin, tu élimineras.

source: TEXT_BANAMA307_01248_YADOVVGAH_000_010<tab>There is no greater disgrace than that which has been inflicted upon the dead. Should you be taken, you will receive no quarter.
target: TEXT_BANAMA307_01248_YADOVVGAH_000_010<tab>Placer les <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E892A0302 /var> aux <var 33 ((EObj)) 0DF61E91050302 /var> à Zahar'ak, tu vas. Un affront plus humiliant que la mort, exposer au grand jour ces prises de guerre constituera pour eux.
TEXT_BANAMA307_01248_AMALJAA_000_011<tab>Les armes qu'on nous a volées, ce sont<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANAMA307_01248_YADOVVGAH_000_020<tab>The Flamefangs weep for their dishonored brothers! They curse us; they hate us. More importantly: they fear us!
target: TEXT_BANAMA307_01248_YADOVVGAH_000_020<tab>Ta mission, tu as réussi. Le plan, tu as habilement mené à bien. Le goût amer de l'injure suprême, ils doivent à l'heure actuelle savourer.

source: TEXT_BANAMA307_01248_YADOVVGAH_000_021<tab>Break a warrior's body, and he will thirst for vengeance. Break his spirit, and he will clamor for peace. Judge my methods distasteful if you will─but know that I seek to end this conflict, not prolong it.
target: TEXT_BANAMA307_01248_YADOVVGAH_000_021<tab>Le privilège de ceux qui veulent la paix, subjuguer son adversaire sans le blesser est. L'arme de ceux qui ont compris ce qu'est la force suprême, détruire le moral de l'ennemi est donc. De toujours chercher à briser sa volonté de combattre, notre stratégie est donc<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANAMA307_01248_POP_MESSAGE<tab>A mournful cry echoes across the desert...

target: TEXT_BANAMA307_01248_POP_MESSAGE_000_000<tab>Action impossible. Vous devez d'abord abattre tous les ennemis.
